sample.description: Interphase HeLa cell (ATCC CCL-2) overexpressing mApple-TNFa-RUSH, frozen 8 min post 50 μM biotin addition.
sample.protocol: High pressure freezing, freeze-substitution resin embedding with 1% OsO<sub>4</sub> 0.1% UA 3% H<sub>2</sub>O in acetone; resin embedding in Eponate 12.
sample.contributions: Sample provided by Aubrey Weigel (HHMI/Janelia), prepared for imaging by Gleb Shtengel (HHMI/Janelia), with imaging and post-processing by C. Shan Xu (HHMI/Janelia).
